content: I don't have access to the specific contact information for the business clubs at the university of pennsylvania. however, i can suggest that you visit the website of the university's business school or the website of the office of student affairs to find a list of clubs and organizations for business students. you can also reach out to the university's student services department for assistance in connecting with the appropriate groups or clubs. additionally, individual club representatives usually have contact information publicized on their respective social media or university-affiliated pages, which a search engine can deliver.
